TURING TEST:
Goal:
To determine whether a machine can behave like a human in conversation.

Components:
1. Interrogator: 
  >Human judge
  >Sends questions to two participants
2.Human Participant:
  >Real human answering questions
3.AI Agent:
  >Chatbot/AI system generating responses
4.Communication Interface
  >Text-based system
  >Prevents judge from knowing who is human
5.Evaluation Module
  >Judge decides which participant is human

Architecture:

User Interface (Chat Window)
        │
        ▼
Interrogator / Judge
        │
 ┌──────┴───────┐
 ▼              ▼
Human          AI Agent
Participant     NLP Model

