CAPTCHA:
Goal:
Differentiate human users from bots.

Components:
1.Client Interface:
  >Website form
  >Displays CAPTCHA:
2.CAPTCHA Generator
  >Generates distorted text/image:
3.Challenge Database
  >Stores correct answers temporarily:
4.Verification Engine
  >Compares user input with correct answer
5.Bot Detection Logic
  >Rate limits or blocks bots
